snippet.title: COACH FIGHT! | Beat the Beat
snippet.description:
Link to play: https://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/918229
Coach Fight! is a new music rhythm game where you step into the gloves of a skilled boxer delivering knockout punches to the beat. Choose your coach, step into the ring, and hit those notes to win the fight.

Credits:

• hbystuff: https://hbystuff.newgrounds.com/
